Jane Novak https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Novak 0 Jane Novak (January 12, 1896 – February 3, 1990) was an American actress of the silent film era. She was the sister of actress Eva Novak, and niece of actress Anne Schaefer. Jane_Novak ( January_12_,_1896 – February_3_,_1990 ) was an_American_actress of the_silent_film_era .
